videos.description: Clock issues cause delays to start Syracuse versus Pitt; players and coaches are frustrated.

videos.description: Syracuse goes with the full-court press for a spark that finishes with another steal and a dunk from Michael Gbinije to cap a 14-2 run.
videos.headline: Press and dunk caps Syracuse run to tie the game

videos.description: With Syracuse down one point with just over six seconds left, Trevor Cooney's shot at the buzzer doesn't fall giving Pittsburgh the 72-71 win.
videos.headline: Pitt survives when Cooney's shot falls short
